::Dollen::

        Dollen calmed his rage and ran over to where KitKat and GoldenEye
were.

        "Ah, but who's going to cover YOU my dear?" Dollen said to GoldenEye
smiling.  Dollen turned around, and fired another missile at Rizopas.  He
then looked at KitKat.

          "Hello, commander.  It's an honor to meet you," he said and fired
of another missile at Deemos.
